OL,2,MTekhnē-cal Village
OL,4,E-2.378171671045834,52.04028161496325
OL,6,GA village for people who like playing
OL,7,Gwith string. Loosely organised
OL,8,Gfibrecrafts themed village, with a
OL,9,Gcentral marquee with places to sit,
OL,10,Gtea/coffee, and free craft materials.
OL,11,GAll crafting ability levels welcome!
OL,12,GWe will run drop-in crafting sessions
OL,13,Gfor all ages and another fibrecraft
OL,14,Gmaterials swap again this year. The
OL,15,Gvillage will be very family and LGBTQ+
OL,16,Gfriendly, and we will do our best to
OL,17,Gbe a calm sensory space for anyone who
OL,18,Gneeds a break away from the main
OL,19,Gareas.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
